{"tid":1254931,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【美洲盃】美斯︰另一個美洲盃現在開始","createTime":"2019-06-24T10:08:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-27T05:25:57.000Z","uid":43785,"like":5,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"cb8250af8e14e27186851be8ea05483119f2abf1","tid":1254931,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T10:08:06.000Z","msg":"【美洲盃】膺MOM迎32歲生日　美斯︰另一個美洲盃現在開始<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5UDC4iu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5UDC4iu.jpg&h=67c9634b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n阿根廷周日以2:0擊敗卡塔爾的美洲盃分組賽，美斯雖然沒有入球進賬，但踢足全場並且在組織上發揮作用的這名巴塞隆拿球星賽後當選為這場比賽的最佳球員（MOM）。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n2CDOLz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn2CDOLz.jpg&h=3e36181e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n周一32歲生日的美斯在帶領阿根廷以小組次名晉級8強後表示︰「最重要的是取勝，繼續留在美洲盃、通過分組賽階段。這對即將來臨的（比賽）將是很重要的推動力&hellip;&hellip;另一個美洲盃現在開始。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mT4Zyb1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmT4Zyb1.jpg&h=1b3aca05&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n美斯坦言︰「我們需要一場勝利來給予我們信心和平靜，我最喜歡的是球隊的態度和贏取比賽的慾望。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/J2gk15n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ2gk15n.jpg&h=a8dc8b3f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0654d7fade1c9093ae9d5b7af9e668c2eda430f7","tid":1254931,"uid":124891,"like":36,"dislike":2,"score":34,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T10:11:16.000Z","msg":"帶領阿根廷以小組次名晉級8強<br />\n佢做左啲乜？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14b7327c3c301ab2998e6ede0d906d16222fd145","tid":1254931,"uid":58880,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"0654d7fade1c9093ae9d5b7af9e668c2eda430f7","tid":1254931,"uid":124891,"like":36,"dislike":2,"score":34,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T10:11:16.000Z","msg":"帶領阿根廷以小組次名晉級8強<br />\n佢做左啲乜？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/so